### Healthcheck
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/

### Members - List
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/members

### Members - Create
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/members
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ada Lovelace",
  "email": "ada@example.com",
  "role": "admin",
  "image_url": null,
  "team": "Core"
}

### Members - Show
# ID yerine member_id kullanılır
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/members/1

### Members - Update (PUT)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/members/1
